This paper focuses on adapting systems of learned representations, specifically in convolutional neural networks, as they switch from performing one task to another. This topic is highly relevant to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
